text: #CovidVaccine shots are supposed to be free. You are not supposed to be billed directly for the shots or any fees. If billed, notify the provider or report them to the U.S. Office of the Inspector General by calling 1-800-HHS-TIPS or visit https://t.co/W5ZwKAN2Vb.
